name: clock with no hands
description: A self explanation by an architect and artist from karachi "hasam waraich", who couldn't able to change his habit of getting late even in the significant moments of his life , this artwork consist of 10 signed editions, a clock with no hands : "i am always late, whether i have to get somewhere or to do anything, even if i have to say anything no matter what, i am just a clock with no hands".
